c: 10
v: 49
t: "Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna andinamandla akwenza bubi esiqwini sam, kungekho nzuzo ndinokuzizuzisa yona ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande (ukundenza kona).” Sizwe ngasinye sinexesha esilibekelweyo, lisakufika ixesha (elo) labo abangekhe balilibazise bengekhe balikhawulezise nangeyure (enye)"